ck;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"수정된 bio의 모습\"\n        title=\"수정된 bio의 모습\"\n        src=\"/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/f058b/0_bio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/c26ae/0_bio.png 158w,\n/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/6bdcf/0_bio.png 315w,\n/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/f058b/0_bio.png 630w,\n/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/40601/0_bio.png 945w,\n/static/4f3f898db9fb343d6a62bdd9d8ebae1f/35252/0_bio.png 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이와 같이 스타터를 조금씩 수정하는 것만으로 편하게 사이트를 제작할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"github-pages로-배포하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#github-pages%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"github pages로 배포하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Github Pages로 배포하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"github-저장소-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#github-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"github 저장소 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Github 저장소 생성</h3>\n<p>Github Pages를 만들기 위해 먼저 Github 저장소를 생성합니다. 저장소의 이름을 아무렇게 하면 url이 <code class=\"language-text\">[사용자이름].github.io/[프로젝트이름]</code>이 되기 때문에 프로젝트 이름이 붙지 않는 url을 사용하고 싶으면 저장소 이름을 <code class=\"language-text\">[사용자이름].github.io</code>로 해주세요.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/daed9/0_github_repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.30379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"깃허브 저장소 생성\"\n        title=\"깃허브 저장소 생성\"\n        src=\"/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/f058b/0_github_repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/c26ae/0_github_repo.png 158w,\n/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/6bdcf/0_github_repo.png 315w,\n/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/f058b/0_github_repo.png 630w,\n/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/40601/0_github_repo.png 945w,\n/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/78612/0_github_repo.png 1260w,\n/static/badca8f874ea4cd89dba336ec44a3d66/daed9/0_github_repo.png 1426w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>저장소를 생성했으면 블로그 폴더를 원하는 branch에 push합니다. Gatsby를 빌드하면 파일이 어지러워지기 때문에 저처럼 main branch가 깔끔하길 원하시다면 소스코드를 main으로, 빌드된 파일을 deploy라는 branch로 관리해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"command-line-prompt\"><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span></span><span class=\"token function\">git</span> init\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> commit -m <span class=\"token string\">\"first commit\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> branch -M main\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote remove origin\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">add</span> origin <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>깃_주소<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> push -u origin main</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"블로그-빌드-배포\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%B9%8C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC\" aria-label=\"블로그 빌드 배포 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>블로그 빌드, 배포</h3>\n<p>gh-pages를 설치합니다. gh-pages는 원하는 branch에 Github Pages를 배포할 수 있도록 도와주는 모듈입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"command-line-prompt\"><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span></span><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gh-pages --save-dev</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>deploy라는 branch를 Github Pages로 쓰겠습니다. 다음 줄을 package.json의 scripts에 추가해주세요. 블로그를 build한 뒤 deploy라는 branch에 푸시하라는 스크립트입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">package.json</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ...\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby build &amp;&amp; gh-pages -d public -b deploy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    ...\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>스크립트를 설정하면 다음 명령어로 Gatsby 사이트를 Github Pages에 배포할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"command-line-prompt\"><span data-user=root data-host=localhost></span></span><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run deploy</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>깃허브 저장소 Settings에서 Github Pages의 source branch를 build 파일이 푸시된 branch로 설정하고 저장합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/913a1/0_branch_setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.39240506329114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"깃허브 페이지 브랜치 설정\"\n        title=\"깃허브 페이지 브랜치 설정\"\n        src=\"/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/f058b/0_branch_setting.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/c26ae/0_branch_setting.png 158w,\n/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/6bdcf/0_branch_setting.png 315w,\n/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/f058b/0_branch_setting.png 630w,\n/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/40601/0_branch_setting.png 945w,\n/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/78612/0_branch_setting.png 1260w,\n/static/d4a9bcbe8c8e8b853c162a2628356ea2/913a1/0_branch_setting.png 1476w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>배포된 Github Page는 <code class=\"language-text\">https://[사용자이름].github.io/</code>로 접속할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/d9ed5/0_github_page.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.65822784810127%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"greenblues1190.github.io\"\n        title=\"greenblues1190.github.io\"\n        src=\"/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/f058b/0_github_page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/c26ae/0_github_page.png 158w,\n/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/6bdcf/0_github_page.png 315w,\n/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/f058b/0_github_page.png 630w,\n/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/40601/0_github_page.png 945w,\n/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/78612/0_github_page.png 1260w,\n/static/7d7b459061990101561b85c0df5c22e9/d9ed5/0_github_page.png 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"커스텀-도메인-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%A4%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%80-%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"커스텀 도메인 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.