레코드를 생성하기 위해 <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/pages/configuring-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site/managing-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site\">다음 IP 주소</a>를 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">185.199.108.153\n185.199.109.153\n185.199.110.153\n185.199.111.153</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/9eaa0/0_dns_records.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.0126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"DNS Records\"\n        title=\"DNS Records\"\n        src=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/f058b/0_dns_records.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/c26ae/0_dns_records.png 158w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/6bdcf/0_dns_records.png 315w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/f058b/0_dns_records.png 630w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/40601/0_dns_records.png 945w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/78612/0_dns_records.png 1260w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/9eaa0/0_dns_records.png 1676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"gatsby-plugin-cname으로-cname-생성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-cname%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-cname-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin cname으로 cname 생성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-cname으로 CNAME 생성하기</h3>\n<p>Github Pages를 통해 배포를 하다보면 <a href=\"https://github.com/tschaub/gh-pages/issues/213\">Github Pages에서 설정한 커스텀 도메인이 초기화되는 문제</a>가 발생합니다. Github가 CNAME 파일을 참고하기 때문인데요. CNAME을 생성하는데는 다음과 같은 방법들이 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">public</code> 폴더에 <code class=\"language-text\">CNAME</code> 파일 생성</li>\n<li>npm 스크립트에 <code class=\"language-text\">echo &quot;customdomain.com&quot; &gt; build/CNAME</code> 추가</li>\n<li><strong>gatsby-plugin-cname 사용</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>그 중 첫번째와 두번째 방법은 커스텀 도메인이 바뀔 때마다 직접 수정을 해야하는 불편함이 있습니다. <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-cname/\">gatsby-plugin-cname</a>은 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>에서 siteUrl을 읽어와 자동으로 CNAME을 생성해주는 유용한 플러그인입니다. 아래 명령어로 설치합니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-plugin-cname</code></p>\n<p>플러그인 설치 후 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 파일에 다음을 추가합니다. <code class=\"language-text\">npm run deploy</code>로 배포 시, <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 파일의 siteUrl을 읽어 자동으로 CNAME이 생성됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-diff-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-diff-javascript\">module.exports = {\n<span class=\"token unchanged language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> siteMetadata<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n</span><span class=\"token deleted-sign deleted language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix deleted\">-</span>    siteUrl<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://greenblues1190.github.io/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>    siteUrl<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://your.custom.domain/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"token unchanged language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-cname</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"token unchanged language-javascript\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n</span>}</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%EB%AA%A9%ED%91%9C\">개발 목표</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#gatsby-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gatsby 시작하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#gatsby-cli-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">Gatsby Cli 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#gatsby-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%ED%84%B0-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D\">Gatsby 스타터 선택</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#gatsby-configuration\">Gatsby Configuration</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#github-pages%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Github Pages로 배포하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#github-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">Github 저장소 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%B9%8C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC\">블로그 빌드, 배포</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#%EC%BB%A4%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%80-%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">커스텀 도메인 설정</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">도메인 등록</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#a-%EB%A0%88%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">A 레코드 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/0-blog-deploy-custom-domain/#gatsby-plugin-cname%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%